org.apache.archiva.components.graph.base

Class SimpleNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.archiva.components.graph.base.SimpleNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<SimpleNode>, Node<SimpleNode>

    public class SimpleNode
extends Object
implements Node<SimpleNode>, Comparable<SimpleNode>
    Simple node implementation. The hash value is based on the id. Comparation is by label, if exists, otherwise by id.
